      "content": "but that's the thing... you actually said it. a burden. i look at the math of it all and it just doesn't add up. every month we fall further behind because i can't earn enough, and all they get from me is stress and more bills. it feels like if i wasn't even here, the money they spend on me and the stress i cause would just... disappear. they could actually breathe.",
